fdf9edba-b2c8-11ed-8fc0-e74518d3deae.description: Deployment Frequency is a measure of how often a team successfully releases or deploys code to production. For the Elite performing teams, deployment frequency is greater than multiple deploys per day, the High is between once per day and once per week, the Medium is between once per week and once per month, and the Low is less than once per month
